  "title": "refactor(html): migrate default templates to VDOM",
  "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\nThis PR migrates the default templates from Hogan.js to VDOM, and adds missing tests for them.\r\n\r\nThis is necessary before deprecating Hogan.js, to avoid triggering a warning when using default templates.\r\n\r\n## Next steps\r\n\r\nThis PR revealed a number of issues with our current tests and some of our types. I limited the changes and fixes to keep the PR focused and legible, but we should tackle it to avoid slowing down future features.\r\n\r\nI filed it as [technical debt](https://algolia.atlassian.net/l/cp/1t8Hz40B) so we can keep track of it.",
